text: Khin Yu May (, ; 23 March 1937 - 23 January 2014) was a Burmese actress. She was a two-time Myanmar Academy Award winning actress and singer. She was known for her roles in A-Thet, I Bawa We, and in Equal Love. May died on 23 January 2014 at the age of 77 in Yangon, Burma. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1937 births Category:2014 deaths Category:Burmese actors Category:Movie actors Category:Singers
